The paper focuses on neural network architecture design and optimization, which is a core topic in machine learning and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates its proposed methodology on image classification tasks, which falls under the sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of evolutionary search and pruning techniques also suggests a potential fit for the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and control systems (cs.SY).
